    "plain_content":  "Having trouble viewing this email? Try this link. ( {{weblink}} )\n\n*WHY EVERYONE IS DRINKING OUR BRAIN BOOSTING INSTAMIX*\n\nStrong coffee, big promises. What is brain boosting coffee and is it really better with butter? Find out why it\u0027s become the most-ordered drink on the menu and how it might provide benefits to your daily life.\n\nRead Now → ( http://www.google.com )\n\n*PHIL GOES TO COLOMBIA*\n\nOur founder, Phil, went on his quarterly trip to Antioquia, Colombia. He visited our Caffe family to see how the crop is coming and help with bean harvesting for the cafe. Read on to learn the tradition and journey behind every bean in your morning pick-me-up.\n\nRead Now → ( http://www.google.com )\n\n*ENJOY AT HOME*\n\nLove Phil’s Caffe? Get your favorite brew delivered to your doorstep through our online store, or stop buy the cafe to pick up a bag. We’ll grind it fresh for you!\n\n*Kenya 2* ( http://www.google.com )\nMedium Roast\n$12.99\n\n*Colombia Hazelnut* ( http://www.google.com )\nMedium Roast\n$11.99\n\nVisit us at philscaffe.com ( http:// )\n\n( http://www.google.com ) ( http://www.google.com ) ( http://www.google.com )\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} ) - Unsubscribe Preferences ( {{{unsubscribe_preferences}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://sendgrid.com/ )",
